.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball, handball, badminton, golf
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, iris, zinnia, aconite, balloon-flower
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
The people use 5 different means of transport: surfingmaster, bike, car, ship, subway
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. the person who growslily is the person who's sport is handball
2. the person who growsswedish is the owner of the dog
3. the person who growsiris is the person drinking tea
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person drinking coffee
6. the person driving the car is the owner of the bird
7. the person who's sport is golf is the person driving the bike
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person who growsaconite is on the far left
10. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the owner of the horses is on the left or right of the person driving the bike
12. the person driving the surfingmaster is the person drinking beer
13. the person who growszinnia is the person driving the ship
14. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing
15. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
